title: Tata Motors global wholesales up 9 pc in Q3
description: Tata Motors global wholesales, including that of Jaguar Land Rover went up by 9 per cent year-on-year to 3,38,177 units in the December quarter. Global wholesales of Tata Motors' commercial vehicles and Tata Daewoo range in October-December period of FY24 were at 98,679 units, up 1 per cent over third quarter of FY23, the company said in a regulatory filing.
